Levels of Testing- end to end - acceptance testing - primarily happy path. - integration - any two units tested together - for us, it means we are going to test through the service interface (HTTP) - and to the attached resources which will be test doubles.- unit testing - testing individual units of code (a method, etc) - isolated from dependencies - cannot use: - databases - networks - file system - clocks - etc.- static testing - using your language, linters, etc.
